@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pkmymr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.72) / 0.09) * v0)
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    v1 = v2
    v2 = 0.61
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.03) + (v2 + 0.44 + v0 + 0.81)) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.47) / (v0 + 0.44 + v0 + 0.74)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    tmp = 0.07
    data[tid] = v0
